<plot>Bill Selvitella is a happily married middle-aged man who learns, quite without warning, that he has mere weeks to live. Determined to face fate bravely and responsibly, he makes his arrangements, and then throws himself a funeral party... where he meets someone who challenges his conception of how he's lived his life thus far, and how he should spend his final days.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046031</url></doc>
